title: Will a Pixel 4a activated after 06/01/21 would still have the unlimited high quality photos storage?
content: I wanted to know if a Pixel 4a activated after June 1, 2021 would still have the unlimited high quality photos storage. I have ordered one but it is taking awhile before I get it. It is probable that I would get it after June 1. So I wanted to know if I would still get the unlimited Google Photos storage perk.
